{"tid":1176833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美據報警告港勿與中國昆侖銀行持有運伊朗石油輪往來","createTime":"2019-05-29T12:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T09:26:53.000Z","uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc53fa7b5d8aa213beffc96b49c94e787d38bd39","tid":1176833,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"美據報警告港勿與運伊朗石油輪往來 2019/05/29 06:11<br />\n美國據報敦促香港政府，不要與一艘運載伊朗石油的油輪有業務往來，否則可能違反美國制裁令，面臨懲罰。 <br />\n<br />\n彭博引述美國高級官員表示，一艘名為 Pacific Bravo 的油輪正駛往香港，提醒香港政府不能讓油輪靠岸，及不得允許當地公司向船隻提供服務，以免違反美國制裁令。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國官員指， Pacific Bravo 由中國昆侖銀行持有。路透社去年報道，昆侖銀行是中國與伊朗交易的主要渠道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/549458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F549458&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=2d3f95cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F549458&h=768e8bd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/549458</a>"},{"pid":"7ed2e565236bd800ce9d608a4ecfa259c9397bcf","tid":1176833,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}